{"tid":244794,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"時間停止器....","createTime":"2017-05-15T16:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T01:27:56.000Z","uid":23552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86d4297fd865aee497576ed42749034134f51af7","tid":244794,"uid":23552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"呢件事發生係我中學時代....<br />\n<br />\n果日我如常咁準備返學<br />\n<br />\n點知呢一日做乜都唔順利<br />\n<br />\n首先明明較咗十幾個鬧鐘<br />\n<br />\n我一次都聽唔到 搞到勁晏先出門口 <br />\n<br />\n返學途中啲紅綠燈勁耐先轉一次<br />\n<br />\n都唔緊要 都總算趕得切<br />\n<br />\n返到課室諗住拎啲功課出嚟做埋佢 仆你個街 點知冇帶<br />\n<br />\n唉 都算 唔撚驚 最多留堂 <br />\n<br />\n一直等 一直等 終於等到放學 拿拿林做埋啲功課就諗住返屋企打下機啦<br />\n<br />\n點知返到屋企樓下嘅商場 有個30幾歲帶眼鏡嘅呀叔問我依家幾多點<br />\n<br />\n點知我一拎部電話出嚟 就比佢搶走咗 我諗住追 不過廢事 陣間唔夠人打可能仲比人姦埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉 好撚嬲啦 諗住發洩下 <br />\n<br />\n就係我行緊轉角位想揮拳發洩嘅時候"},{"pid":"1d900eae2bffed320ef95f05262628a087f9dadf","tid":244794,"uid":23552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"一個年約三十歲嘅女人就走三係我面前 <br />\n<br />\n我嚟唔切反應 一嘢揸咗落佢對波到<br />\n<br />\n嗯～～～～～好舒服<br />\n<br />\n好軟熟 好有彈性 <br />\n<br />\n我比十分"},{"pid":"c9d4197f08b1ad1085611dc3c460a8874d5655ac","tid":244794,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2156dbd10f27b9581515885c3941f26c1619283d","tid":244794,"uid":79050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:02:17.000Z","msg":"正皮是比個故名的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51efe41c7f765bb7eee54e7a9c14e28ee85eaa44","tid":244794,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T00:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee32b6803b6adbfab980546ceaae11cda5019a65","tid":244794,"uid":98884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"